caption:
8th at @challengegrancanaria and happy to start the season with my 1st middle distance top 10 on my second attempt. 
🏊Right at the front in the swim exiting 4th and happy with how I navigated the bike 🏍️ coming in with the front pack behind the breakaway. 
🏃Run could have been better but more so due to my current bike legs than my current run form which I’m quite happy with. 

Some really exciting news coming which in a way could have been a slight distraction from the race, but also makes performing well quite sweet also. I’ll tell all in due course.
